text: Just saw an article about these "repair cafes" in NYTimes.  Seemed like something folks here might be interested in:

attachments.title: Repair PDX - Working Together to Fix Things in Portland, OR - Repair Cafés
attachments.text: We organize repair cafés – free events that bring volunteers who like to fix things together with people who have broken items that need fixing.
